author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Its been a strange week in entertainment. We have a Captain America who isn't American, a Star Trek movie everyone hated, and the most insane cope ever for The Acolyte's failure. Join me, MauLer, Despot of Antrim, Ryan Kinel and Chris Gore as we talk about all this and more. 

Subscribe to Despot: https://www.youtube.com/@DespotofAntrim
Subscribe to Ryan: https://www.youtube.com/@ryankinel-rkoutpost1
Subscribe to Chris: https://www.youtube.com/@FilmThreat
title: Open Bar #128 - Captain Anti-America, Star Trek Disaster, Acolyte's Epic WIN?
